{"type": "article", "id": 30172, "title": "能当作背包使用的购物袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160726214638aT74wQUJDmxvCBtZ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>2013 年，Adnan Alicusic 设计了一款既能当作背包又可以折叠成小口袋的购物袋 <a href=\"http://www.notabag.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Notabag</a>，这个独一无二的产品不仅在众筹上获得了成功，还赢得了 2016 年的德国设计奖的杰出产品设计奖。今天要介绍的 Reflective Notabag 是它的迭代产品，为了更好地在夜晚保护使用者的安全，为购物袋加入了反光材料。起初这只是 Notabag 与瑞典的自行车配件品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bookman.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BOOKMAN</a> 合作的限量产品，在收到不错的反馈之后，它们决定进行大批量生产，并且为这个系列加入了更多的颜色选择。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/adnanalicusic/be-seen-be-safe-the-reflective-bag-and-backpack\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 25 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726214703eERBzYaIu4AZwthf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726214703BMRgoZw0hUNFpE2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.501471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726214703O3ryowvgKnqClVep.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726214703cW2K3vawyUkYn9Ip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561300\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}